title: [Curlew Brook, Swimming Dock]
description: Crafted of wide modwir planks, this dock juts out into the deep waters of the Mistydeep, allowing swimmers easy access to the deeper flows of the river.  A dragonfly perches on the narrow boardwalk leading westward, back to shore.
